  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the grill to medium-high heat.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together soy sauce, garlic, and ginger.",
    "Add the beef heart pieces to the bowl and marinate for at least 30 minutes.",
    "Thread the marinated beef heart pieces onto skewers.",
    "Grill the anticuchos for 3-4 minutes per side, or until cooked to an internal temperature of 145 degrees.",
    "Meanwhile, melt the beurre monte in a saucepan over low heat.",
    "Add the shredded mozzarella cheese to the saucepan and stir until melted and smooth.",
    "Serve the anticuchos on a lazy Susan spinner with the cheesy beurre monte sauce, diced Korean pear, and a sprinkle of salt and pepper."
